{"timestamp": "2025-12-04 08:51:51.338071", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission summary:\n- Anomaly detected: Yes\n- Faulty device(s): host_1_1_1_1\n- Root cause: host_missing_ip\n\nRationale:\nThe diagnosis report shows host_1_1_1_1 has its interface up at L2 but no IPv4 address, no default route, and cannot reach any network resources. The distribution switch and upstream OSPF core are healthy, confirming the issue is isolated to the host’s missing IP configuration.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 1909, "output_tokens": 102, "total_tokens": 2011, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 0}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
